  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Only if set Debug to On when system language is Russian: launch app and type some sum for send command -> crash.\r\nIt also happens after changing system language back to English and restarting device.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nCan type sum and send \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\napp is closed, no message about app crash. \r\n\r\nlog contains \r\n```E audit   : type=1701 msg=audit(1500567977.290:262): auid=4294967295 uid=10182 gid=10182 ses=4294967295 subj=u:r:untrusted_app:s0:c512,c768 pid=13102 comm=\"pool-4-thread-3\" reason=\"memory violation\" sig=6```\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\nvideo: \r\ncrash 1: https://drive.google.com/open?id=0Bz3t9zSg1wb7azJZNlpxLXlhcjg\r\ncrash 2: https://drive.google.com/open?id=0Bz3t9zSg1wb7cGtWMjM0QV9QLUE\r\ncrash 3: https://drive.google.com/open?id=0Bz3t9zSg1wb7bFhaQXJaUFl1RVk\r\n- Connect device to the computer with USB cable\r\n- change device language to Russian\r\n- open Status, so its UI is in Russian\r\n- Open Console\r\n- send Debug /On command (there is open #1479 on wrong messages shown)\r\n- close app\r\n- launch app again\r\n- open group chat\r\n- tap on send command, select  some valid recipient \r\n- On Fee screen: type 0,001 -> crash\r\n\r\n### Logs\r\nWas reproduced at least 3 times:\r\ncrash 3: [log12345crash.log.txt](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/1163026/log12345crash.log.txt)\r\ncrash 2: [log1234crash.log.txt](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/1163028/log1234crash.log.txt)\r\ncrash 1: [log123crash.log.txt](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/1163027/log123crash.log.txt)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop 0.9.8-85-gcad5e0c5+\r\n* Operating System: \r\nReal device Samsung Galaxy S6, Android 6.0.1\r\n",
